  "remarks": "Passport no: Philippines number AA780554. Title: \"Amir\". Founder and leader of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128) and linked to the Abu Sayyaf Group (QDe.001). In detention in the Philippines as of May 2011.  Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Photos included in INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/un/1523805.; Listing: Listed on: 4 Jun. 2008 (amended on 13 Dec. 2011, 25 Oct. 2016, 22 Sep. 2017, 24 Nov. 2020)",
